snippet.title: Twins the Game for Windows
snippet.description:
DOWNLOAD THE GAME HERE:
http://bit.ly/29qgzjS

Night and day, black or white. Jump between the two worlds, find your twin soul and resist in this deadly spiky world. 

Twins is a free highly addicting minigame, very much the popular like the Ketchapp iOS publisher. Game Trooper’s intention is to release a collection of high quality very addicting minigames.
